{"PageNumber":8,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":1620,"Width":2880,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  Public key cryptography","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":315},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":182},"RightBottom":{"X":1492,"Y":315},"RightTop":{"X":1492,"Y":182}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"![](222,454,261,497) Bob has two keys: a private key, $S_B$ , which Bob keeps secret, and a public key, $P_B$ , which Bob broadcasts widely","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":683},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":435},"RightBottom":{"X":1844,"Y":683},"RightTop":{"X":1844,"Y":435}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/2536963a828e52c3628ad0a83c999eb1-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● In order for Alice to send an encrypted message to Bob, she needs only obtain Bob's public key, $P_B$, and use that to encrypt her message, M, and send the result, $C = E_{P_B}(M)$, to Bob.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":1134},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":712},"RightBottom":{"X":1806,"Y":1134},"RightTop":{"X":1806,"Y":712}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● Bob then uses his secret key to decrypt the message as $M = D_{S_B}(C)$","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":1332},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":1149},"RightBottom":{"X":1737,"Y":1332},"RightTop":{"X":1737,"Y":1149}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● That is, separate keys are used for encryption and decryption","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":219,"Y":1514},"LeftTop":{"X":219,"Y":1350},"RightBottom":{"X":1812,"Y":1514},"RightTop":{"X":1812,"Y":1350}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"figure","Text":"","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":1844,"Y":1131},"LeftTop":{"X":1844,"Y":653},"RightBottom":{"X":2840,"Y":1131},"RightTop":{"X":2840,"Y":653}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"figure_text","Text":"graph TD     A[Sender] --> B[encryption]     A --> C[ciphertext]     A --> D[private]     A --> E[key]     B --> F[Attacker]     B --> G[eavesdropping]","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":1844,"Y":1131},"LeftTop":{"X":1844,"Y":653},"RightBottom":{"X":2840,"Y":1131},"RightTop":{"X":2840,"Y":653}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":0,"group_type":""}],"ImagePath":"images/83f23c4f2e3cc3b9b621efd51f3a10c5-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}